snippet.title: Careers in Cyber Threat Intelligence - Oliver Fairbank (Orpheus Cyber) | CREST Careers Evening
snippet.description:
At CREST's Careers Advice evening, Oliver Fairbank (Head of Analysis, Orpheus Cyber & CTIPs Executive Committee member) talks about the routes into Cyber Threat Intelligence and why it's a fulfilling career path.

CREST Threat Intelligence Professionals group:
https://www.crest-approved.org/crest-threat-intelligence-professionals/index.html

Watch more videos about Threat Intelligence here:
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZ2XFVIKjM5uklDnXXNe8_DRm2KvczYvO

Orpheus Cyber:
https://orpheus-cyber.com/

Find out more about CREST:
https://www.crest-approved.org/
